Program: Great Lives
Title: Lady Hester Stanhope
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b00djvgk
Last Broadcast Date: Fri 3 Mar 2017
Series of biographical discussions with Matthew Parris. Georgian political hostess, traveller, diplomat and spy Lady Hester Stanhope is nominated by businesswoman and Dragon's Den investor Deborah Meaden. Stanhope's biographer Kirsten Ellis lends her expert knowledge to the discussion.